trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection> class represents the `providers` element within a configuration file.

The following code example shows how to iterate through the <xref:System.Configuration.ProtectedConfigurationSection.Providers%2A> property, which returns a <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何逐一查看<xref:System.Configuration.ProtectedConfigurationSection.Providers%2A>屬性，它會傳回<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings" /> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings" /> 物件加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Add%2A> method to add a <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Add%2A>方法，將<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings>物件加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Clear%2A> method to remove all <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings> objects from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Clear%2A>方法移除所有<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings>從集合的物件。

trans-unit.source: Accesses an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 存取 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection" /> 類別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Use this method to access a specified <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings> object contained within this <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: 使用這個方法來存取指定<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings>物件包含在這個<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection>類別。

trans-unit.source: A string reference to the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings" /> object within the collection.
trans-unit.target: 集合中 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings" /> 物件的字串參考。

trans-unit.source: Gets an item from the collection.
A <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings" /> object contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 包含在集合中的 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value at the specified index in the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定位於 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection" /> 集合中所指定索引處的值。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Item%2A> property to get or set a specified <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings> object contained within this <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Item%2A>屬性來取得或設定指定<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings>物件包含在這個<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection>類別。

trans-unit.source: Removes an element from the collection.
Use the <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Remove%2A> method to remove a specified <xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings> object from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection.Remove%2A>方法中移除指定<xref:System.Configuration.ProviderSettings>集合中的物件。
